  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Math Master</strong> is a small educational math game inspired by retro games. Practice basic math while improving your calculator. Improve with each practice, earn all the achievements and show other players that you deserve to be at the top of the leaderboard. Follow your path to becoming a <strong>Math Master</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/b5a0c99e999337f27d462753b6e041b8.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blocks with operations will be generated at the top of the screen for the player to solve. During the game, these blocks will fall. If you accumulate more blocks than allowed or make more mistakes than allowed, the game will end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/35b91c0dc3cba583cdb1ea51eb3a2e21.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All</strong> operations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>addition</strong> operations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>subtraction</strong> operations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>multiplication</strong> operations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>division</strong> operations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/a711ace8448524600dfe574fa1763a77.poster.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/a711ace8448524600dfe574fa1763a77.webm?t=1735908816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achieve all goals</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get all <strong>40</strong> achievements and all <strong>28</strong> available stickers. Enjoy and stick some stickers on the wall. ♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/444b43387250503359f85467d51df015.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online leaderboards:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are more than 5 online leaderboards available. Improve your mathematical reasoning and achieve the necessary score to be among the best. Have your name visible on the leaderboard for all mathematical players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/3eda15c8847e87900e13d80d566bb787.poster.avif?t=1735908816\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/3eda15c8847e87900e13d80d566bb787.webm?t=1735908816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/3eda15c8847e87900e13d80d566bb787.mp4?t=1735908816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge other players locally:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up a tournament to play locally against your friends and family. The tournament works on a match-based format. In each round, each player will have the chance to demonstrate their skills in a match.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Math Master</strong> is a small educational math game inspired by retro games. Practice basic math while improving your calculator. Improve with each practice, earn all the achievements and show other players that you deserve to be at the top of the leaderboard. Follow your path to becoming a <strong>Math Master</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/b5a0c99e999337f27d462753b6e041b8.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blocks with operations will be generated at the top of the screen for the player to solve. During the game, these blocks will fall. If you accumulate more blocks than allowed or make more mistakes than allowed, the game will end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/35b91c0dc3cba583cdb1ea51eb3a2e21.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All</strong> operations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>addition</strong> operations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>subtraction</strong> operations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>multiplication</strong> operations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>division</strong> operations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/a711ace8448524600dfe574fa1763a77.poster.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/a711ace8448524600dfe574fa1763a77.webm?t=1735908816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achieve all goals</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get all <strong>40</strong> achievements and all <strong>28</strong> available stickers. Enjoy and stick some stickers on the wall. ♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/444b43387250503359f85467d51df015.avif?t=1735908816\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online leaderboards:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are more than 5 online leaderboards available. Improve your mathematical reasoning and achieve the necessary score to be among the best. Have your name visible on the leaderboard for all mathematical players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/3eda15c8847e87900e13d80d566bb787.poster.avif?t=1735908816\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/3eda15c8847e87900e13d80d566bb787.webm?t=1735908816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296240/extras/3eda15c8847e87900e13d80d566bb787.mp4?t=1735908816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge other players locally:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up a tournament to play locally against your friends and family. The tournament works on a match-based format. In each round, each player will have the chance to demonstrate their skills in a match.</p>",
